Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me from back then... {Yesterday's me. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:37.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}couldn't understand the concept of getting along with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me from back then... {Yesterday's me. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}couldn't understand the concept of a person living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:00:59.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.64,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:19.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:21.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:23.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:27.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That small encounter made a big difference in the path that I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:32.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believed that those fun times {will}would always continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:35.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For breaking the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't remember it well. {I really can't remember it well. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chirp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:06.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:11.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:17.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you are feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that I'd like to talk about. {There is something that I'd like to talk about. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With me... Would you like to try and write a novel? {Comment: Do we really need the "With me."? Or is this "Would you lkike to try and write a novel with me?" - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking such things? {Why are you asking such things? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask? {Why, you ask?- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because it sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you ask? {Why, you ask? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:57.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun knows that I can only retain thirteen hours of my memory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, but I would also help and- {Yes, but I would also help and- - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to write it.{I would not like to write it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you teasing me like this? {Why are you teasing me like so? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Teasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You were much more kind before. {You were much more kinder before. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:17.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try writing a novel for Chihiro. {I wanted to try my hand at writing a novel for Chihiro. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:25.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you said that writing stories was your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the me from a week ago. {myself, from a week ago. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if it was a week ago or today. {It doesn't matter if it was a week ago or today. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And dreams are dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back. {I'm going back. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:49.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just feel kind of lost... about you. {I hate it when they do on liner flash backs, I have to go back and dig out the script from before to find the line =_=}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's true alright. {alright - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:54.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:03.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So you broke our promise and went to see Miyamura-senpai instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's exchange manga for this week.{check}{I thought this more to "Let's exchange manga for this week"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't bought it yet.{I got "I haven't bought it yet"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:28.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh! But senpai is in charge of buying the {\i1}Mimi{\i0} monthly magazine.{I got "Eh! But Senpai's is in charge of buying the "Mimi" monthly publications" assuming "mimi" is the manga title}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can just read ahead.{check} {I got "You can just read ahead"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Write it for me, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money left over this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I had to lend some to Hiro-senpai already.{the money}{I had to lend some to Hiro-senpai already. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Onii-chan...?{borrow the money}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like Hiro-senpai got dumped by Miyamura-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:50.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I paid for Hiro-senpai because he didn't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand what you are saying. {I really don't understand what you are saying. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:07:01.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, Hiro-senpai made Miyamura-senpai angry, so she left first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That means Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:08.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai even with looks is not good with girls. {Even Hiro-senpai doesn't look like he's good with girls. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It flies so well even though it's so light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the money will come any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:34.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, err... Miyako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No adding the '-san' at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't answer next time. {if he calls her with 'san' or with Miyamura} {I won't respond the next time you do that. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:39.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right. {Alright. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:45.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But because of your honesty, I'll forgive you this time. {Because of you honesty, I'll specially forgive you this time. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know, it's emergency food in case of a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the month, being in debt is always an emergency. {At the end of the month, being in debt is always an emergency. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That seems lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:06.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really will pay this time, so let's go and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You think I play around every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, to Hirono-kun's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:33.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the month so there definitely won't be anything decent left to eat. {for hirono}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That girl without a doubt was Hirono's...{That girls was doubtlessly Hirono's... }{That girl was certainly Hirono's... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:57.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You live in a pretty decent house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a little lacking on awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,First off, you're a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:07.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just barge into a bachelor's house on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun is a person who will be nice to me. {Hirono-kun is a person who will be nice to me. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:18.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know, your mind is way too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden change in topic?{check}{"What's with that backtracking?" or "What's with that sudden topic change", I prefer second one}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:26.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd understand a girl that I don't know personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:30.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know what kind of person that person is, and what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:31.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not to be arrogant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I have good eyes for knowing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's because, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because what?{W-What is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I found a perverted book!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're interested in these types.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They're just magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:54.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start working right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just observe quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't show other people the manuscript before publishing. {You can't just show the manuscript to people before publishing. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then show it to me after it is published.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:09.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow the manga that Hirono-kun made. {Comment: Changed mangas to manga - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll return it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to make a trade for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let... me... see...{if possible, the 'let' and the 'me' and the 'see' show seperately}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a short piece that I drew before publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I only have the copy because I don't have the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:28.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miss President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my camera. {I'll take my camera. - megu}{Check on this.. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:37.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Call me when you don't have any materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There'll most likely be trouble during the next project.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Cine-Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:50.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They're really looking forward to it, so they'll definitely win. {They are really anticipating it, so they'll win definitely.}{- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you filming it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There is a picture I must take no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty arrogant question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the level where it will cause injuries when eaten. {It's at the level where I may cause health problems when eaten. - megu} {Akiko jammu? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did you have to do to make such bad-tasting food? {Just what did you have to do to make such bad tasting food? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really need to put it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:38.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is just one, rice shouldn't be wasted like this. {suggection: "rice shouldn't be made/handled poorly like this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not one, it's three.{the rice balls}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There were three made.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,These were the ones that were finished.{The ones that were done were these.}{These are the ones that were finished. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other two that are left?{I thought she daid "Where is the last one?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They just left my hand when I grabbed them.{It left my hand when I grabbed it.}{check} {I think it's "It just left my hand"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:56.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-senpai should never cook again.     {suggestion: "Kei-senpai shouldn't waste food like that!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But first of all, why are you acting like this all of a sudden?{But firstly, why are you being like this suddenly.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To suddenly be cooking... It's not like you, Senpai. {To suddenly cook... it's not like you Sempai. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,even I have things like responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why Onii-chan is working so hard is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,partly because of me.{Partly my fault.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is also interesting.  {oh my god, are they introducing the little boy with yaoi manga?!?}{Well, he DOES draw shoujo manga now... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:26.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Read it, read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It looks exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Draw more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan might be a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me from back then... enjoyed being with Onii-chan. {Myself, back then... who enjoyed being with Onii-chan. - megu} {Myself can also be "Yesterday's me" - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:13:00.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me from back then... enjoyed seeing them both happy. {Myself, back then... who enjoyed seeing them both happy. - megu} {ditto. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The me of now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that I'm searching for? {Today's me... what am I yearning for? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The lacking color in the world that I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To find that, I... {To find that, I... - megu}{Check here. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, Hirono-kun... {Besides that, Hirono-kun / Beside you, Hirono-kun - I have little idea.. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drawing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, but... {It's not that, but... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The manga that Hirono-kun drew. {The manga that Hirono-kun drew. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,About three more short pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's in publishing up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:48.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Was my manga that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you look nervous. {Hirono-kun, you look nervous. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you might be a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:26.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The pork cutlet won't fully cook on the inside even though I cook it completely. {The pork cutlet won't get completely fried, even though I heated it long enough. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's something wrong with the pan?{check}{"...pot"} {Maybe there's something wrong with the pot? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is Senpai's fault.{always thought it's senpai instead of senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being mean and tell me already.{Don't be mean and tell me.}{Stop being mean and tell me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:36.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For fried food, the temperature of the oil...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The pan is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:46.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Water, water, water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't use water! Don't ever use water!{Water is a no, water is a definite no!/Don't use water, never use water!}{The latter sounds better. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The fire will just spread more! {The fire would just spread more! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mayonnaise, put in mayonnaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Squirt it all into the pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Squirt it you say? O-Okay, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:04.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:08.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's out.{the fire}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's out, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly genius! {Amazing! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something amazingly genius! {It's not just something amazing! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing short of a miracle.{It's a record.}{It's nothing short of a miracle! - megu}{I couldn't think of any other superlative, so yeah. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:28.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be,"Welcome back." {It shouldn't be "welcome back". - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:32.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop putting the spare key under the flower pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As thanks for letting me borrow your manga...{As a return for the manga.}{As thanks for letting me borrow your manga... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of making dinner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:41.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Go home! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:47.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that humans can't digest raw starch? {Don't you know that humans can't digest raw starch? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:52.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that intake of excessive artificial flavoring will cause numbing of the hands and feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:59.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I made the decision to never eat anything a girl made for the rest of my life. {I promised myself to never eat anything a girl cooked for the rest of my life. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you have some kind of painful memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything unnecessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,These things I can eat with a peace of mind. {This, I can eat with peace of mind. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako's special herb rice is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Do you want to taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:28.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:35.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it... I didn't want to admit that to this girl. {Dang it, I didn't want to admit this to her. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:37.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To hear that it's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,makes it all worth it.{cooking it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as fulfilling when you eat alone.{There is no relevance if you eat alone.}{It's not as fulfilling when you eat alone. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, you say? What about your family? {Alone, you say? What about your family? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a no-no, Hirono-kun. {That's a no-no, Hirono-kun. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding your chopsticks weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since you are Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:53.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you should hold your chopsticks properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have tenosynovitis on my right hand.{check}{ "...tenosynovitis..."}{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenosynovitis}{First time I've heard of that.. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. It's something like a work-related injury.{Don't mind, it's something like job injury.}{It's alright. It's something like a work-related injury. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just some minor symptoms. {There are just slight symptoms. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when I just endure the pain while I'm drawing, but...{There are times when I draw enduring the pain but.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:20.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sleep, eat, play, or go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What I...?{What, you say?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:30.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like an idiot who is pushing himself by doing what he's not fit for? {Do I look like an idiot who keeps on pushing himself by doing something that he's not fit for? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:41.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To work diligently... there is value just in that. {To work diligently is a good thing. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun isn't a idiot. {Hirono-kun isn't foolish. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold the chopsticks well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'll feed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to work, you need to rest your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Ahh~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. I said it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. Ahh~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:19.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it. The novel. {Let's try it. The novel. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You said that it was your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you had a story that you wanted to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that you are saying something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that you are saying something cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:53.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm someone whose time has stopped.{Because I'm a person whose time has stopped. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:56.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have anything to do, nor do I have anything I want to do. {Because I don't have anything to do, nor anything I want to do. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So to make my dreams come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Such...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Simple... {seperate lines if possible}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:10.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It is as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is wrong is me. {I'm the one who's wrong. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:20.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you telling me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Why would a person other than myself want to know about me?! {Why would a person other than me know about myself? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:59.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, I want to write about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The dream... Before the memories disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all that is left.{Is all that there is left.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I absolutely don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:08.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:12.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't even do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:16.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It'll turn out that I can't do anything. {It'll turn out that I can't do anything. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:18.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kisses are for lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we be lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:37.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun today is mean, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:38.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been all right if it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I slept alone yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to meet with Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,because I liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's me... wrote it in the diary. {Yesterday's me... wrote in the diary. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the Renji-kun of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not that I don't really like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just please hold me for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hold you? {A hug? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because it's warm.{check} {"Yes, it's warm"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:14.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The story that Chihiro wants to write... what is it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're very persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:17.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I'm thinking of writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is in a world where everything came to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The story of a solely surviving girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:03.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:07.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:10.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.31,0:23:14.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:21.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Senpai. It's not good if you don't put anything in it.{It's not good senpai, if you don't put anything.}{Sempai, it's not good if you don't put anything. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:23.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The bread and the vegetables-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:30.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that's connected... {Comment: This line and the next doesn't make much sense. "The thing that connects..." "Is a sad story." - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,is a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:43.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1}ef - a tale of memories:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:44.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Outline.{\i0}
